::Epyon::

"Well, if he came in with a Maximal we'll trust him for now. But if he
gets out of line put him in the brig. I feel nervous with non- Maxi's on
board."
He sat back thinking about his problems. He had one crew members help
captive by Decepticons, one not reporting, both of whitch he was waiting
to talk with Prowl about. He also had to get the ship ready for the
Maximal City project. Wizard was also being quiet. Did he not agree with
the city plan?
